            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use the back of a spoon to make 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> small wells in the tomato sauce</p><p>Crack the<strong> eggs</strong> into the wells</p><p>Tear the remaining <strong>'Nduja</strong> over the tomato sauce (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook, covered, for 5-6 min further or until the eggs are cooked to your liking</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
